{"tid":1186381,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【讚】壞車司機揮紅布","createTime":"2019-06-05T01:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T12:26:40.000Z","uid":66242,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ecd19d1585b86ee2f8007c435857722ffb703c","tid":1186381,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"今朝七點半<br />\n沙壢公路出九龍<br />\n威爾斯後面<br />\n嗰度有個彎位又少車<br />\n不嬲都快嘅<br />\n點知彎位後面慢線有個阿叔企喺度揮紅布<br />\n佢身後壞車<br />\n我覺得真係要讚<br />\n因為高架天橋附近無位俾佢避<br />\n佢坐喺車內都危險<br />\n嗰個環境落車揮紅布係比較安全嘅做法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋今朝都好熱好曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3308c15a4421f1f5655bcabc10b705360aef4fb3","tid":1186381,"uid":191815,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"行入路邊先安全<br />\n連反光衣都冇 仲夠膽係後面打交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時遇到啲盲閪連命都冇 仲要畀網民話你抵死<br />\n仲有人讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23144a4e4d0a696e341fee77140e079a880957ce","tid":1186381,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3308c15a4421f1f5655bcabc10b705360aef4fb3","tid":1186381,"uid":191815,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"行入路邊先安全<br />\n連反光衣都冇 仲夠膽係後面打交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時遇到啲盲閪連命都冇 仲要畀網民話你抵死<br />\n仲有人讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"天橋<br />\n右彎<br />\n佢左線<br />\n基本上已經企得最埋路邊<br />\n當場無更好嘅地方避<br />\n除非你話留喺車"},{"pid":"c07a30256876a3c7d878750237f030e10f3f7fb6","tid":1186381,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23144a4e4d0a696e341fee77140e079a880957ce","tid